th you more and done some raids with you =) I'll miss you Mord.<br><br>Banann Shadowstalker 59 uber paladin<br><br>&lt;Eclipse of Norrath&gt; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub30.ezboard.com/uanathae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Anathae</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sentinent Member</span><br>  Posts: 98<br> <font color=#333333>(2/1/01 5:40:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub30.ezboard.com/fthesentinentfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Final Farewell</span><hr size=1> ghah, you will be missed, mord<br><br>Ana/Elizae <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub30.ezboard.com/bthesentinent.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=monarch>Monarch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sentinent Member</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#333333>(2/1/01 9:51:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub30.ezboard.com/fthesentinentfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Final Farewell</span><hr size=1> Um, kinda dont know what to say.  Speechless.  I do however know I want to thank you for allowing me to be part of this great guild you created and lead.  And I also know you and your colleagues put together a place that actually gave meaning to playing EQ other than becoming uber and camping something that will just repop anyways after it's defeated.  Although we've hardly interacted, time I spent hunting and raiding with you was time well spent.  Just thought Id let you know that.<br> <br>Before I close, I have to say your feelings on EQ not being fun to play anymore isnt solitary.  Ive been thinking the samething myself lately.  Im not sure if it's the people, and yes, pe